    public interface TestRun
extends Task<TestRunDto>
    Test Run A Test Run bundles multiple Test Tasks (@see TestTask). A Test Run object can be started by submitting it to the TaskPoolRegistry (see TaskPoolRegistry.submitTask(Task)).
